lead_paragraph: Sam Querrey beat Rajeev Ram 6-4, 7-6 (8-6) on Sunday in an all-American final in the Delray Beach Open for his eighth ATP World Tour title and first since 2012.

headline.print_headline: Sam Querrey Beats Rajeev Ram in Delray Beach Open Final
